sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP TLS 1.2+
    participant Activator as Knative Activator /<br/>Queue Proxy<br/>8012/TCP mTLS
    participant Caikit as Caikit transformer-container<br/>8080/TCP HTTP | 8085/TCP gRPC
    participant TGIS as TGIS kserve-container<br/>8033/TCP gRPC (localhost)
    participant S3 as S3 / PVC<br/>Model Storage
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>User Workload Monitoring

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    Gateway->>Activator: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8012, mTLS<br/>Auth: Istio PeerAuthentication
    Activator->>Caikit: HTTP/8080<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)<br/>Auth: PeerAuthentication STRICT
    Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC/8033 (localhost)<br/>Plaintext (loopback)<br/>Auth: None
    TGIS->>S3: Load model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / S3 credentials
    S3-->>TGIS: Model weights
    TGIS-->>Caikit: Inference result (gRPC)
    Caikit-->>Activator: JSON response
    Activator-->>Gateway: Forward response (mTLS)
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: gRPC call (TextGeneration)<br/>HTTPS (h2)/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    Gateway->>Activator: Forward request<br/>gRPC/8012, mTLS<br/>Auth: Istio PeerAuthentication
    Activator->>Caikit: gRPC (h2c)/8085<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)<br/>Auth: PeerAuthentication STRICT
    Caikit->>TGIS: gRPC/8033 (localhost)<br/>Plaintext (loopback)<br/>Auth: None
    TGIS-->>Caikit: Inference result (gRPC)
    Caikit-->>Activator: gRPC response
    Activator-->>Gateway: Forward response (mTLS)
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Prometheus,Caikit: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Scraping
    Prometheus->>Caikit: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8086<br/>PERMISSIVE mTLS (no cert required)
    Caikit-->>Prometheus: Caikit runtime metrics
